# 📚 Class 02 - Date: 03 July 2025
## E-Commerce Brand Management & Marketing  
**Institute:** DIGI MARVIX  

---

## 🔍 Professional Terms & Marketing Metrics

| Term   | Full Form                | Urdu Explanation                          |
|--------|--------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Matrix | Data Framework           | مختلف ڈیٹا کو سمجھنے کا طریقہ               |
| KPI    | Key Performance Indicator| کارکردگی جانچنے کا معیار                   |
| ROI    | Return on Investment     | سرمایہ کاری پر حاصل ہونے والا فائدہ       |

---

## 📊 Performance Metrics

| Metric | Formula                                | Urdu Explanation                            |
|--------|----------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------|
| ACOS   | (Ad Spend / Ad Revenue) × 100          | اشتہارات پر خرچ / آمدنی کا فیصد              |
| CPM    | (Total Ad Spend / Reach) × 1000        | فی ہزار صارفین تک پہنچنے کی لاگت             |
| CTR%   | (Clicks / Impressions) × 100           | کتنے لوگوں نے اشتہار دیکھا اور کلک کیا       |
| CR%    | (Conversions / Clicks) × 100           | کلکس کے مقابلے میں خریداری کرنے والوں کی شرح |

---

## 📱 Facebook Ads Terminology

| Term       | Description                          | Urdu Explanation                          |
|------------|--------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Click      | Unique Click on Ad                   | ہر فرد کا کلک (منفرد)                     |
| Impression | How many times ad is shown           | اشتہار کتنی بار نظر آیا                   |
| Audience   | Total number of people targeted      | کل نشانہ بنایا گیا ہدف                     |
| Traffic    | Visitors from ads to website         | اشتہار سے ویب سائٹ پر آنے والے لوگ         |
| Rate       | Any performance or percentage metric | کوئی بھی شرح (فیصد)                       |

---

## 🌐 DIGI MARVIX: Website Insights

| Concept               | Explanation in English                       | Urdu Explanation                                   |
|-----------------------|----------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------|
| Data Driven Marketing | Marketing strategies based on collected data | ڈیٹا کی بنیاد پر مارکیٹنگ حکمتِ عملی                  |
| Projects              | Business goals and action-based tasks        | کاروباری مقاصد کو حاصل کرنے کے لئے اقدامات           |
| Forecast              | Estimate or plan for future trends           | مستقبل کا اندازہ لگانا                             |
| Prediction            | Analytical guess about future events         | کسی چیز کا تجزیہ کرکے رائے دینا (تبصرہ)             |

---

## 🎯 Types of Marketing

| Type                  | Urdu Explanation                            |
|-----------------------|---------------------------------------------|
| Precision Marketing   | درست اور مخصوص صارفین کو ٹارگٹ کرنا         |
| Personalized Marketing| ہر صارف کی ذاتی پسند کے مطابق اشتہار         |
| Performance Marketing | نتائج پر مبنی مارکیٹنگ جیسے CTR, CR, ROI     |

---

## 🎯 Marketing Funnel Stages

| Funnel Stage  | Description         | Urdu Explanation                          |
|---------------|---------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Top Funnel    | Awareness Building  | صارف کو برانڈ کے بارے میں آگاہ کرنا      |
| Middle Funnel | Engagement          | صارف کو دلچسپی لینا اور تعلق قائم کرنا    |
| Lower Funnel  | Conversion          | خریداری یا ایکشن لینا                    |

---

### ✅ Top Funnel (Awareness)

- Brand Awareness Videos  
- Problem-solving Content  
- Introductory Offers  

### ✅ Middle Funnel (Engagement)

- Focused Messaging  
- Product Benefits + Promotion  
- Brand Features Highlight  
- Social Proof (Reviews, Testimonials)

### ✅ Lower Funnel (Conversion)

- Direct Call-to-Action  
- Discounts / Urgency  
- Limited Time Offers

---

## 🚀 Performance Must-Haves (For Ads)

- Brand Name in Caption  
- Clear, Simple Message  
- Visible Branding (Logo, Colors)  
- Optimized for Sound-off (No Sound Needed)  
- Branding from First Second  
- Motion Billboard (Quick, Eye-catching visuals)  
- Mobile-Optimized Content  
- Strong CTA Button (Buy Now, Learn More)

---

## 📈 Marketing Strategy Steps (Step-by-step)

1. Identify the Problem  
2. Create a Story Around It  
3. Make Customers Feel They Belong  
4. Present the Solution  
5. Pitch the Product Clearly  

> 📊 **Note:** 78% product pitches happen during the **repair/problem** phase.

---

## 🏬 B2C vs D2C Marketing

### 🔸 B2C (Business to Consumer)

- BTM2C Module  
- Mass Traffic Required  
- Pricing Sensitivity  
- Platform Restrictions  
- Referral Fees  
- Documentation Requirements  
- PPC (Pay Per Click) Ads + Social Media Marketing

### 🔹 D2C (Direct to Consumer)

- No third-party interference  
- Brand has full control over sales, messaging, and customer experience
